    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>WP Remote Thumbnail is a very lightweight WordPress plugin that comes with zero configuration and one-click setup. Using this plugin, you can easily set any external image as the featured image of any post/page or even custom post types.</p>\n<p>This plugin automatically adds a custom metabox to each post type that supports post thumbnails. You just need to copy and paste the URL of any image into the metabox and click publish/update.</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/28J9IYZ4WFI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Go to your admin area and select Plugins -&gt; Add new from the menu.</li>\n<li>Search for &#8220;WP Remote Thumbnail&#8221;.</li>\n<li>Click install.</li>\n<li>Click activate.</li>\n<li>Go to any post/page and add your external images.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='what%20is%20a%20remote%20thumbnail%3F'>\nWhat is a remote thumbnail?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can call a remote thumbnail an external featured image. This plugin will help you set any external image as the featured image of any post/page.</p>\n</p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: url save issue</li>\n<li>Checked with updated wordpress version 6.6</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Fatal and warning errors</li>\n<li>Checked with latest wp and PHP version</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Meta data URL save issue.</li>\n<li>Code cleanup.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with larger images.</li>\n<li>Increased timeout for getting images.</li>\n<li>Better error handling.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>This is the first version.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "A small lightweight plugin to set external/remote images as post thumbnail/featured image.",
    "description": "<p>WP Remote Thumbnail is a very lightweight WordPress plugin that comes with zero configuration and one-click setup. Using this plugin, you can easily set any external image as the featured image of any post/page or even custom post types.</p>\n<p>This plugin automatically adds a custom metabox to each post type that supports post thumbnails. You just need to copy and paste the URL of any image into the metabox and click publish/update.</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/28J9IYZ4WFI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n",
